resources.summary: Managed Applications are built using other Azure services like Compute, Storage, Networking, SQL etc. You will be charged for the underlying Azure services included in your application.
resources.note: Managed Applications are built using other Azure services like Compute, Storage, Networking, SQL etc. You will be charged for the underlying Azure services included in your application. Additionally, the publisher of the Application may have a monthly charge for software, support, and services included with the application. This additional charge will show up as a separate line item in the bill.
